@NODE ManPages "Manual Pages"

    PNM UTILITIES

    @{"PNM" link pnm}            Portable anymap file format.  No actual file format,
                   the pnm programs operate on ppm, pgm and pbm files.

    PNM General

    @{"PNMALIAS" link pnmalias}       Antialias a portable anymap.
    @{"PNMARITH" link pnmarith}       Perform arithmetic on two portable anymaps.
    @{"PNMCAT" link pnmcat}         Concatenate portable anymaps.
    @{"PNMCOMP" link pnmcomp}        Composite two portable anymap files together.
    @{"PNMCONVOL" link pnmconvol}      General MxN convolution on a portable anymap.
    @{"PNMCROP" link pnmcrop}        Crop a portable anymap.
    @{"PNMCUT" link pnmcut}         Cut a rectangle out of a portable anymap.
    @{"PNMDEPTH" link pnmdepth}       Change the maxval in a portable anymap.
    @{"PNMENLARGE" link pnmenlarge}     Read a portable anymap and enlarge it N times.
    @{"PNMFILE" link pnmfile}        Describe a portable anymap.
    @{"PNMFLIP" link pnmflip}        Perform one or more flip operations on a portable
                   anymap.
    @{"PNMGAMMA" link pnmgamma}       Perform gamma correction on a portable anymap.
    @{"PNMHISTMAP" link pnmhistmap}     Draw a histogram for a PGM or PPM file.
    @{"PNMINDEX" link pnmindex}       Build a visual index of a bunch of anymaps.
    @{"PNMINVERT" link pnminvert}      Invert a portable anymap.
    @{"PNMMARGIN" link pnmmargin}      Add a border to a portable anymap.
    @{"PNMNLFILT" link pnmnlfilt}      Non-linear filters: smooth, alpha trim mean, optimal.
    @{"PNMNORAW" link pnmnoraw}       Force a portable anymap into plain format.
    @{"PNMPAD" link pnmpad}         Add borders to portable anymap.
    @{"PNMPASTE" link pnmpaste}       Paste a rectangle into a portable anymap.
    @{"PNMROTATE" link pnmrotate}      Rotate a portable anymap by some angle.
    @{"PNMSCALE" link pnmscale}       Scale a portable anymap.
    @{"PNMSHEAR" link pnmshear}       Shear a portable anymap by some angle.
    @{"PNMSMOOTH" link pnmsmooth}      Smooth out an image.
    @{"PNMTILE" link pnmtile}        Replicate a portable anymap into a specified size.
 
    Convert From PNM

    @{"PNMTODDIF" link pnmtoddif}      convert a portable anymap to DDIF format.
    @{"PNMTOFITS" link pnmtofits}      Convert a portable anymap into FITS format.
    @{"PNMTOPS" link pnmtops}        Convert portable anymap to PostScript.
    @{"PNMTORAST" link pnmtorast}      Convert a portable pixmap into a Sun rasterfile.
    @{"PNMTOSGI" link pnmtosgi}       Convert a portable anymap to a SGI image file.
    @{"PNMTOSIR" link pnmtosir}       Convert a portable anymap into a Solitaire format.
    @{"PNMTOTIFF" link pnmtotiff}      Convert a a portable anymap into a TIFF file.
    @{"PNMTOXWD" link pnmtoxwd}       Convert a portable anymap into an X11 window dump.

    Convert To PNM

    @{"ANYTOPNM" link anytopnm}       Attempt to convert an unknown type of image file to a
                   portable anymap.
    @{"FITSTOPNM" link fitstopnm}      Convert a FITS file into a portable anymap.
    @{"GIFTOPNM" link giftopnm}       Convert a GIF file into a portable anymap.
    @{"PSTOPNM" link pstopnm}        Convert a PostScript file into a portable anymap.
    @{"RASTTOPNM" link rasttopnm}      Convert a Sun rasterfile into a portable anymap.
    @{"SGITOPNM" link sgitopnm}       Convert a SGI image file to a portable anymap.
    @{"SIRTOPNM" link sirtopnm}       Convert a Solitaire file into a portable anymap.
    @{"TIFFTOPNM" link tifftopnm}      Convert a TIFF file into a portable anymap.
    @{"XWDTOPNM" link xwdtopnm}       Convert a X11 or X10 window dump file into a portable
                   anymap.
    @{"ZEISSTOPNM" link zeisstopnm}     Convert a Zeiss confocal file into a portable anymap.


    PPM UTILITIES

    @{"PPM" link ppm}            Portable pixmap file format.  Lowest common denominator
                   color image file format.

    PPM General

    @{"PPM3D" link ppm3d}          Convert two portable pixmap into a red/blue 3d glasses
                   pixmap.
    @{"PPMBRIGHTEN" link ppmbrighten}    Change an images Saturation and Value from an HSV map.
    @{"PPMCHANGE" link ppmchange}      Change all pixels of one color to another in a portable
                   pixmap.
    @{"PPMDIM" link ppmdim}         Dim a portable pixmap down to total blackness.
    @{"PPMDIST" link ppmdist}        Simplistic grayscale assignment for machine generated,
                   color images.
    @{"PPMDITHER" link ppmdither}      Ordered dither for color images.
    @{"PPMFLASH" link ppmflash}       Brighten a picture up to complete white-out.
    @{"PPMFORGE" link ppmforge}       Fractal forgeries of clouds, planets, and starry skies.
    @{"PPMHIST" link ppmhist}        Print a histogram of a portable pixmap.
    @{"PPMMAKE" link ppmmake}        Create a pixmap of a specified size and color.
    @{"PPMMIX" link ppmmix}         Blend together two portable pixmaps.
    @{"PPMNORM" link ppmnorm}        Normalize the contrast in a portable pixmap.
    @{"PPMNTSC" link ppmntsc}        Make a portable pixmap look like taken from an American
                   TV.
    @{"PPMPAT" link ppmpat}         Make a pretty pixmap.
    @{"PPMQUANT" link ppmquant}       Quantize the colors in a portable pixmap down to a
                   specified number.
    @{"PPMQUANTALL" link ppmquantall}    Run ppmquant on a bunch of files all at once, so they
                   share a common colormap.
    @{"PPMQVGA" link ppmqvga}        8 plane quantization.
    @{"PPMRELIEF" link ppmrelief}      Run a Laplacian relief filter on a portable pixmap.
    @{"PPMSHIFT" link ppmshift}       Shift lines of a portable pixmap left or right by a
                   random amount.
    @{"PPMSPREAD" link ppmspread}      Displace a portable pixmap's pixels by a random amount.

    Convert From PPM

    @{"PPMTOACAD" link ppmtoacad}      Convert portable pixmap to AutoCAD database or slide.
    @{"PPMTOBMP" link ppmtobmp}       Convert a portable pixmap into a BMP file.
    @{"PPMTOGIF" link ppmtogif}       Convert a portable pixmap into a GIF file.
    @{"PPMTOICR" link ppmtoicr}       Convert a portable pixmap into NCSA ICR format.
    @{"PPMTOILBM" link ppmtoilbm}      Convert a portable pixmap into an ILBM file.
    @{"PPMTOMAP" link ppmtomap}       Extract all colors from a portable pixmap.
    @{"PPMTOMITSU" link ppmtomitsu}     Convert a portable pixmap to a Mitsubishi S340-10 file.
    @{"PPMTOPCX" link ppmtopcx}       Convert a portable pixmap into a PCX file.
    @{"PPMTOPGM" link ppmtopgm}       Convert a portable pixmap into a portable graymap.
    @{"PPMTOPI1" link ppmtopi1}       Convert a portable pixmap into an Atari Degas .pi1 file.
    @{"PPMTOPICT" link ppmtopict}      Convert a portable pixmap into a Macintosh PICT file.
    @{"PPMTOPJ" link ppmtopj}        Convert a portable pixmap to an HP PaintJet file.
    @{"PPMTOPJXL" link ppmtopjxl}      Convert a portable pixmap into an HP PaintJet XL PCL
                   file.
    @{"PPMTOPUZZ" link ppmtopuzz}      Convert a portable pixmap into an X11 "puzzle" file.
    @{"PPMTORGB3" link ppmtorgb3}      Separate a portable pixmap into three portable graymaps.
    @{"PPMTOSIXEL" link ppmtosixel}     Convert a portable pixmap into DEC sixel format.
    @{"PPMTOTGA" link ppmtotga}       Convert portable pixmap into a TrueVision Targa file.
    @{"PPMTOUIL" link ppmtouil}       Convert a portable pixmap into a Motif UIL icon file.
    @{"PPMTOXPM" link ppmtoxpm}       Convert a portable pixmap into an X11 pixmap.
    @{"PPMTOYUV" link ppmtoyuv}       Convert a portable pixmap into an Abekas YUV file.
    @{"PPMTOYUVSPLIT" link ppmtoyuvsplit}  Convert a portable pixmap into 3 subsampled raw YUV
                   files.

    Convert To PPM

    @{"BMPTOPPM" link bmptoppm}       Convert a BMP file into a portable pixmap.
    @{"GOULDTOPPM" link gouldtoppm}     Convert Gould scanner file into a portable pixmap.
    @{"HPCDTOPPM" link hpcdtoppm}      Convert a Photo-CD file into a portable pixmap.
    @{"ILBMTOPPM" link ilbmtoppm}      Convert an ILBM file into a portable pixmap.
    @{"IMGTOPPM" link imgtoppm}       Convert an Img-whatnot file into a portable pixmap.
    @{"MTVTOPPM" link mtvtoppm}       Convert output from the MTV or PRT ray tracers into a
                   portable pixmap.
    @{"PCXTOPPM" link pcxtoppm}       Convert a PCX file into a portable pixmap.
    @{"PI1TOPPM" link pi1toppm}       Convert an Atari Degas .pi1 into a portable pixmap.
    @{"PICTTOPPM" link picttoppm}      Convert a Macintosh PICT file into a portable pixmap.
    @{"PJTOPPM" link pjtoppm}        Convert an HP PaintJet file to a portable pixmap.
    @{"QRTTOPPM" link qrttoppm}       Convert output from the QRT ray tracer into a portable
                   pixmap.
    @{"RAWTOPPM" link rawtoppm}       Convert raw RGB bytes into a portable pixmap.
    @{"RGB3TOPPM" link rgb3toppm}      Combine three portable graymaps into one portable
                   pixmap.
    @{"SLDTOPPM" link sldtoppm}       Convert an AutoCAD slide file into a portable pixmap.
    @{"SPCTOPPM" link spctoppm}       Convert an Atari compressed Spectrum file into a
                   portable pixmap.
    @{"SPUTOPPM" link sputoppm}       Convert an Atari uncompressed Spectrum file into a
                   portable pixmap.
    @{"TGATOPPM" link tgatoppm}       Convert TrueVision Targa file into a portable pixmap.
    @{"XIMTOPPM" link ximtoppm}       Convert an Xim file into a portable pixmap.
    @{"XPMTOPPM" link xpmtoppm}       Convert an X11 pixmap into a portable pixmap.
    @{"XVMINITOPPM" link xvminitoppm}    Convert a XV "thumbnail" picture to PPM.
    @{"YUVSPLITTOPPM" link yuvsplittoppm}   Convert a Y- an U- and a V-file into a portable pixmap..
    @{"YUVTOPPM" link yuvtoppm}       Convert Abekas YUV bytes into a portable pixmap.


    PGM UTILITIES

    @{"PGM" link pgm}            Portable graymap file format.  Lowest common denominator
                   greyscale format.

    PGM General

    @{"PGMBENTLEY" link pgmbentley}     bentleyize a portable graymap.
    @{"PGMCRATER" link pgmcrater}      Create cratered terrain by fractal forgery.
    @{"PGMEDGE" link pgmedge}        Edge-detect a portable graymap.
    @{"PGMENHANCE" link pgmenhance}     Edge-enhance a portable graymap.
    @{"PGMHIST" link pgmhist}        Print a histogram of the values in a portable graymap.
    @{"PGMKERNEL" link pgmkernel}      Generate a convolution kernel.
    @{"PGMNOISE" link pgmnoise}       Create a graymap made up of white noise.
    @{"PGMNORM" link pgmnorm}        Normalize the contrast in a portable graymap.
    @{"PGMOIL" link pgmoil}         Turn a portable graymap into an oil painting.
    @{"PGMRAMP" link pgmramp}        Generate a grayscale ramp.
    @{"PGMTEXTURE" link pgmtexture}     Calculate textural features on a portable graymap.

    Convert From PGM

    @{"PGMTOFS" link pgmtofs}        Convert portable graymap to Usenix FaceSaver(tm) format.
    @{"PGMTOLISPM" link pgmtolispm}     Convert a portable graymap into Lisp Machine format.
